Installation:
1.  Click the "Clone or download" button near the top of this page -> then click “Download Zip”
2.  Open up a Google Chrome browser
3.  Go to the Google Chrome Menu (triple lines) on the top right of the browser -> Then select extensions
4.  Enable developer mode at the top of the extension page
5.  Click “Load Unpacked Extension” -> Find the “CEO-Hunter-Master” file you downloaded in Step 2 and select it
6.  You have officially installed the plugin to use it click on the plugin (the "C" Icon to the right of the URL bar) when you are on the target company’s website
